[thinking] I'm considering adding features like ByteRange, UploadOptions, and ServingUrlOptions to our current blobstore setup since it only covers BlobKey at the moment. I see these features as functional enhancements that could improve our URL option builders for uploads and serving. I believe the interface needs to be public and straightforward for users. Alright, let’s start with the Java approach for implementing this!
